# DTO Rules

## Every field MUST have validation decorators
```typescript
@IsString()
@MaxLength(255)
name: string;

@IsEmail()
email: string;

@IsOptional()
@IsString()
description?: string;
```

## Optional fields need @IsOptional()
```typescript
// CORRECT:
@IsOptional()
@IsString()
nickname?: string;

// WRONG — validation fails when field is undefined:
@IsString()
nickname?: string;
```

## String fields need @MaxLength()
Unbounded strings cause storage issues. Always set a limit.

## Do NOT use @nestjs/swagger decorators
swagger is NOT installed in this project.
